cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language tasks and embedding vectors. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new framework for learning discrete codes and composing embedding vectors. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as these fields also use embedding vectors. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia) as it deals with compressing embedding vectors.
